--- Lokk / Axis / ---

Lokk smiles, and Axis nods.

"Well, it depends. First lets meet the new bots," says Lokk refering 
to Lynxiz, and Termitron. "We'll greet them, then burn around a 
bit," he finishes with a wink. He then strolls over to Lynxiz, 
Termitron, Trinity and Nightlight. "Hello, I'm Lokk, that is Axis," he 
points to Axis, "and the bot over there, is Seekker." He points to 
Seekker. "We're kinda new here and we wanted to say hello." He 
finishes almost nervously.

Lynxiz smiles to herself, "Well, I'm not a Chivitron, I'm a Maximal. 
All of the other bots here are Chivitrons." She doesn't wait up for an 
answer, she continues on to meet up with Termitron.

Lokk catches up to the rest of the group, and repeats what he said.

Axis nudges Seekker, "I hope he hurries up..."
